snippet.title: An Airport for Aliens Currently Run by Dogs - 'Release Date' Trailer
snippet.description:
Dog Airport Game comes to Xbox Series X/S and Steam on May 25th, 2021! A first-person open world comedy adventure across a universe of simulated airports run by stock photo dogs, by the narrative lead of Space Warlord Organ Trading Simulator, Hypnospace Outlaw, and SkateBIRD.

STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1246250/
PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/StrangeScaffold
DISCORD: https://discordapp.com/invite/YySjWvM
TWITCH: https://twitch.tv/WritNelson
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/WritNelson
